Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.20,0:22:36.29,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}Se este mundo está condenado à ruína,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.20,0:22:36.29,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}se kuchiteku sekai naraba
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.29,0:22:39.79,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}se minha vida estiver em perigo,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.29,0:22:39.79,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,[T0][T1]chiriyuku sadame naraba
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.87,0:22:45.38,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}então por que eu deveria viver?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.87,0:22:45.38,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}Se tivesse crido em outra coisa, estaria bem
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:51.05,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}Se não tivesse conhecido você,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:51.05,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}nunca teria sentido essa dor
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.05,0:22:54.47,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}que corta meu peito
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.05,0:22:54.47,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}por dentro, sem nunca saber o que é dor
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.64,0:23:01.06,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}que me separa ao meio
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.64,0:23:01.06,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}por não conhecer a dor
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.52,0:23:03.82,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}É uma requiem grosseira
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.52,0:23:03.82,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}no horizonte do céu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.82,0:23:05.28,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}ressoando até
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.82,0:23:05.28,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}o amanhecer foi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.28,0:23:09.11,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}as alturas do céu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.28,0:23:09.11,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}um requiem ininterrupta
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.11,0:23:11.03,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}e mesmo agora
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.11,0:23:11.03,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}ainda assim ainda
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:12.74,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}em este mundo sem sentido
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:12.74,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}procuro
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.78,0:23:16.16,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}eu busco
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.78,0:23:16.16,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}diferente desde agora
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.16,0:23:18.12,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}por você
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.16,0:23:18.12,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}o que diz respeito a você
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.12,0:23:21.79,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}eu lembro
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.12,0:23:21.79,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}também o prazer de nos encontrarmos
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.79,0:23:25.50,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}o prazer de te encontrar
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.79,0:23:25.50,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}mesmo o frio da morte
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:29.72,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}e a passagem do seu being
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:29.72,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}eu lembro de tudo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.72,0:23:32.80,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}porque eu te amei
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.72,0:23:32.80,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}porque te amei
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.80,0:23:36.56,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}o gelo cresce no meu coração
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.80,0:23:36.56,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}mesmo o mapa do mar que se desvia
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.56,0:23:40.27,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}sobre as feridas dentro de mim
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.56,0:23:40.27,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}nao que restar ferido também
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.27,0:23:44.65,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}eu levarei tudo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.27,0:23:44.65,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}e carregar todo o mal
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.65,0:23:51.66,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}e caminharei pelo meu caminho
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.65,0:23:51.66,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}e seguiria por esta estrada
